<item>
            <title>[THRIFT-2775] static assert fails in src/thrift/internal/ctfe.d</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2775</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;make check in d/lib fails with &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;src/thrift/internal/ctfe.d(94): Error: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt;  (ctfeToString(3.1415) == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;3.1415&quot;&lt;/span&gt;) is &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;because ctfeToString(3.1415) evaluates to &quot;3.14149999999999&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;openSUSE 13.1 (i586)  &lt;br/&gt;
DMD Compiler v2.066.0 &lt;br/&gt;
german locale&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
